  <summary date="2021-07-23T17:49:23Z" status="Introduced in House">Lead Abatement for Families Act of 2021

This bill requires the Department of Housing and Urban Development (HUD) to identify federally assisted housing projects that use lead-based water pipes and allows HUD to award grants for the replacement of these pipes to public housing agencies and other owners.</summary>
